libmt notes
-----------

build.sh	build script
bar		thread barriers
cond		condition variables
conf		[build-time] configuration
lk		bitmap- and other locks
mtx		mutexes (fast and recursive)
priolk		priority locks
sem		semaphores
spin		spin-locks
spinrw		read-write spinlocks
spinwt		velho spin-wait locks
thr		thread API
tktlk		ticket locks

